Student Learning Support
Our student support and resources are tailored to help learners excel in their academic pursuits.
The 'Learning to Learn Better' programme, harnesses the science of learning to empower learners to be effective and fulfilled. Personalised coaching services are also available to discover the best learning approaches and strategies, ensuring learners get the most out of their university experience.
In addition, AdventureLEARN is a self-directed learning platform available to learners. It aids learners in adapting more swiftly and effectively to university-level learning. This platform places its focus on the development of learners in four crucial areas:
Approaches to learning and studying.
Well-being.
Grit and resilience.
Mindset.
